    <doc:div>    
    
    <h2>Community</h2>
    
    <p>See <a href="/how.html">a summary of recent highlights here</a>, but use these forums 
    to keep up to date with all developments:</p>
  
      <div class="col columnLeft">      
      <h3>Mailing list</h3>
      <ul>
	<li>There is a mailing list dedicated to RabbitMQ. Everyone is welcome to join and ask questions 
	    but please make sure your question hasn't been answered before by searching the archives. Two
	    interfaces are available for this:
	    <ul class="plain">
	      <li>A <a onClick="javascript: pageTracker._trackPageview('http://lists.rabbitmq.com/cgi-bin/mailman/listinfo-community');" href="http://lists.rabbitmq.com/cgi-bin/mailman/listinfo">read-only</a> Mailman 
	      interface which also provides information on how to 
	      <a onClick="javascript: pageTracker._trackPageview('http://lists.rabbitmq.com/cgi-bin/mailman/listinfo/rabbitmq-discuss-community');" href="http://lists.rabbitmq.com/cgi-bin/mailman/listinfo/rabbitmq-discuss">subscribe directly</a></li>
	      <li>A <a href="email-archive.html">full web-interface provided Nabble</a> </li>
	    </ul>  
	</li>
      </ul>   
      </div>            
      <div class="col columnRight">      
	<h3>IRC chat</h3>
	<ul>
	  <li>
	  RabbitMQ developers are also sometimes available to chat rabbitmq on irc.freenode.net 
	  (see also <a onClick="javascript: pageTracker._trackPageview('http://freenode.net/-community');" href="http://freenode.net/">http://freenode.net/</a>) in channel 
	  <strong>#rabbitmq -- irc://irc.freenode.net/rabbitmq</strong>. 
	  <p>The logs of these conversations are available here: 
	  <a onClick="javascript: pageTracker._trackPageview('http://dev.rabbitmq.com/irclog/-community');" href="http://dev.rabbitmq.com/irclog/">http://dev.rabbitmq.com/irclog/</a>.</p>
	  <p>You can use this <a onClick="javascript: pageTracker._trackPageview('http://webchat.freenode.net/-community');" href="http://webchat.freenode.net/">web interface to freenode</a> 
	  if you don't have an IRC client installed.</p>
	  </li>
	</ul>
      </div>    
      
      <div class="clear"></div>
 
      <div class="col columnLeft">
	<h3>Bug reports</h3>	
	<ul>
	  <li>To report a bug or problem email <a onClick="javascript: pageTracker._trackPageview('mailto:legitimategrievance@rabbitmq.com-community');"  href="mailto:legitimategrievance@rabbitmq.com">legitimategrievance@rabbitmq.com</a>!
	  </li>
	</ul>
      </div>            
      <div class="col columnRight">
	<h3>Development wiki</h3>
	<ul>
	  <li>
	  We are also working on a development wiki: 
	  <a onClick="javascript: pageTracker._trackPageview('http://dev.rabbitmq.com/wiki/-community');" href="http://dev.rabbitmq.com/wiki/">http://dev.rabbitmq.com/wiki/</a>.
	  </li>
	</ul>
      </div>
      
